---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../../../components/SiteHeader.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../../../components/SiteFooter.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Compare Bath private schools | Overview and A-level metrics"
  description="Build a shortlist of Bath private schools and switch between overview comparisons and A-level metrics, including grades, subject breadth and subject mix."
  canonicalPath="/bath/compare/"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/styles.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/bath-refined.css" />
  </Fragment>

  <a class="skip-link" href="#main">Skip to content</a>
  <SiteHeader minimal={true} />

  <main id="main">
    <div class="shell compare-page">
      <section class="compare-hero">
        <span class="eyebrow">Bath compare tool</span>
        <h1>Compare Bath private schools</h1>
        <p>Build a shortlist of up to four schools, then switch between the core overview metrics and a dedicated A-level view covering grades, subject breadth and subject mix. Your shortlist is saved on this browser so you can come back to it later.</p>
        <div class="compare-actions">
          <a href="/bath/" class="compare-link-button">Back to Bath guide</a>
          <button id="compare-clear-top" class="compare-inline-button" type="button">Clear selection</button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="compare-layout">
        <section class="compare-main">
          <section class="compare-panel">
            <h2>Build your shortlist</h2>
            <p>Select up to four schools to focus the comparison table. If nothing is selected, the full Bath comparison is shown.</p>

            <div id="compare-chooser" class="compare-chooser" aria-label="Choose schools to compare"></div>

            <div class="compare-toolbar">
              <p id="compare-status" class="compare-status" aria-live="polite">Showing all Bath schools.</p>
              <div class="compare-toolbar-actions">
                <button id="compare-clear" class="compare-inline-button" type="button">Clear selection</button>
                <a class="compare-link-button" href="/bath/schools/">View full directory</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div id="compare-pill-row" class="compare-pill-row" aria-live="polite"></div>
          </section>

          <section class="compare-panel">
            <div class="compare-panel-heading">
              <div>
                <h2>Comparison table</h2>
                <p class="compare-panel-lead">Switch between the current overview metrics and the A-level metrics view.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="compare-metric-toggle" role="tablist" aria-label="Comparison table view">
                <button type="button" class="compare-metric-button is-active" data-compare-view="overview" aria-pressed="true">Overview</button>
                <button type="button" class="compare-metric-button" data-compare-view="alevel" aria-pressed="false">A-level metrics</button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p id="compare-table-note" class="compare-table-note">Overview view covers ages, gender, day or boarding format, fees, bursaries and location.</p>
            <div class="compare-table-wrap">
              <table id="compare-table" class="compare-table">
                <thead id="compare-thead"></thead>
                <tbody id="compare-tbody"></tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </section>
        </section>

        <aside class="compare-sidebar">
          <section class="compare-side-card">
            <h3>How to use this page</h3>
            <p>Start with two or three likely options, compare the practical basics, then move into school profiles and open-day planning.</p>
            <ol class="compare-mini-list">
              <li>Select schools above.</li>
              <li>Use the toggle to switch between overview and A-level metrics.</li>
              <li>Open the profile pages for details and open days.</li>
            </ol>
          </section>

          <section class="compare-side-card">
            <h3>What this page is best for</h3>
            <p>This compare tool is designed for first-pass narrowing, not final judgement. It is strongest on factual differences such as age range, boarding format, fees, bursaries and — for senior schools — A-level performance and subject mix.</p>
            <p class="compare-help-note">For fuller context, use the school profiles and open-days guide alongside this page.</p>
          </section>
        </aside>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <SiteFooter />

  <script src="/assets/js/bath-refined.js"></script>
  <script src="/assets/js/compare.js"></script>
</BaseLayout>
